              <strong>Tip:</strong> Minimum hole size drives cost more than most buyers realise. A 0.3 mm drill bit lasts ~3× longer than a 0.2 mm bit before needing replacement. Use 0.3 mm as your default via size unless routing density forces smaller holes.
